{"tid":700662,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"初戀的感覺","createTime":"2018-06-13T13:34:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-13T13:37:18.000Z","uid":189087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7e659d8d556759105ea7ae12315f85d97441df6d","tid":700662,"uid":189087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T13:34:06.000Z","msg":"一次臨記經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n認識一個女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n眼大大 咀細細 樣貌普通<br />\n但上圍都幾豐滿<br />\n傾落ok 唔似港女<br />\n大學畢業 幼稚園老師<br />\n本來諗住收工問佢拎電話<br />\n點知佢趕住去幫人補習 走先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n自此佢一直係我腦海遊走 揮之不去<br />\n茶飯不思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13664a5d097c2284bb77abe8a082a70ef6e60a59","tid":700662,"uid":179571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T13:34:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"47d0eb6f6084c95dbf5292ae5a627fd8536b78f2","tid":700662,"uid":146299,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T13:37:18.000Z","msg":"呢個叫毒撚暗戀的感覺<br />\n唔係初戀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}